OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPetrol driver shortage:    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FVisa scheme planned to ease
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fproblems                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers are working on plans for a   
OL,6, temporary visa scheme to make it easier
OL,7, for foreign lorry drivers to come to   
OL,8, the UK.                                
OL,10,FFinal details of exactly how the       
OL,11,Finitiative will work are expected to be
OL,12,Fannounced this weekend.                
OL,14,FAny changes to immigration rules will  
OL,15,Fbe temporary, with a cap on the number 
OL,16,Fof workers allowed to enter the UK.    
OL,18,FThe shortage of hauliers threatens more
OL,19,Fdisruption to deliveries of petrol,    
OL,20,Ffood and other goods.                  
